{"tid":1283622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣部工作發酵] 大部分支那人開始提走銀行存款和賣股票套現買金","createTime":"2019-07-04T00:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:09:30.000Z","uid":54373,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d40f67ec6bd1930a5ce17cdda9ac86e62c31d5be","tid":1283622,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:48:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.theepochtimes.com/chinese-people-are-buying-gold-taking-money-out-of-banks-and-stock-market_2989072.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.theepochtimes.com%2Fchinese-people-are-buying-gold-taking-money-out-of-banks-and-stock-market_2989072.html&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=daca55ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.theepochtimes.com/chinese-people-are-buying-gold-taking-money-out-of-banks-and-stock-market_2989072.html</a><br />\n<br />\nChinese People Are Buying Gold, Taking Money Out of Banks and Stock Market<br />\nBY OLIVIA LI, EPOCH TIMES<br />\nJuly 3, 2019 Updated: July 3, 2019<br />\n<br />\nChinese people are starting to feel the pressure of economic slowdown. As China&rsquo;s yuan continues to devalue, and several small and medium-sized banks have filed for bankruptcy recently, many Chinese choose to buy gold or take their money out of the bank, to protect their assets. <br />\n<br />\nAdditionally, the Chinese government issued an unusual notice in late June to encourage Party members and cadres to invest in stocks, which is interpreted by many as a desperate move to rescue China&rsquo;s economy."},{"pid":"698416ede858e3882ee071c4352f288e3614c832","tid":1283622,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c80c0b32a54d2d5edcd141a4f2d1b65a823dcd","tid":1283622,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm